Input:
    Policy set Π
    Workload levels P
    Number of runs N

FOR each workload level p ∈ P DO

    FOR each policy π ∈ Π DO

        Initialize empty result list

        FOR run = 1 to N DO
            Set random seed = run
            metrics ← RunSimulation(π, p)
            Store metrics
        ENDFOR

        Compute mean and standard deviation
        Store aggregated results

    ENDFOR

ENDFOR

Export results to CSV

